Gold and silver is on the rise, so looking to to trade gold and/or silver(I can do some cash too) for firearms and maybe optics, parts etc., depending.  Have plenty of firearms, but no or not enough gold and silver??, maybe it's time to diversify, just in case.  I like a bit of everything as long as it's in excellent to new condition(may consider others in "good or fair" condition, depending on the deal/value), so let me know what you have and exactly what you want to do on the deal and we'll go from there.  Sorry for the bad light on the pic, I tried.  A few things I am looking for:
Kel-Tec SU-16C, one or two.
Quality stamped AK-47 with side rail optic mount and with a better trigger than the G2, the Zhukov stock would also be a plus.  The RAS47 looked like a nice package with the nicer trigger group and Zhukov stock, but I've read too many problems with the cast trunnions and bad/faulty rivets.
XDM .45ACP 5.25" model, black or bi-tone model, XDS 9mm black or bi-tone, must be post recall model.
9mm carbine or pistol with folding "arm brace", Beretta CX4 9mm 92FS model or the PX4 model and I can get the adapter, maybe the .45ACP model.  AR 9mm, CZ Scorpion or other?  Really want a nice trigger, so the AR platform will likely be the best value.
FosTech AR Echo trigger.
AR-15 and AR-10 lowers, stripped or complete, prefer stripped because it's much cheaper and I can build them to my taste.  Nice trigger groups and other lower parts.
Optics, Aimpoint, EoTech G33 or Vortex magnifier, 1-2 Primary Arms 1-6x ACSS 5.56/.308 reticle and 1-2 7.62x39 reticle models.
Will consider other firearms etc., in order of preference, semi-autos mostly, then revolvers, tactical shotguns, lever guns and bolt-guns.
Again, let me know exactly what you have and exactly what you want to do on the deal, I will consider and get back to you either way.

Gold:
